{
  "stem": "13817.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Nazi just grabbed it away from his wife and stick it on a bayonet and gave it over to the guy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Here is your baby.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Take her along.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the woman actually was screaming and crying and putting on-- getting on or whatever you would call it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all the Nazi did shot her right there, then and there, and killed her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this husband [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] lost it completely and jumped at that Nazi.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And at the same time, three other guys came with the bayonet and killed him right there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So this was the first impression we got from Auschwitz, or I got.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Other things what happened, which was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two people tried to escape and were caught and brought back into the cam.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To-- to make an example, they put them on-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] tied them up on a-- like a cross and had their arms spread and the legs spread and let them hang there for-- for three or four days until-- until they died.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And coming by there, every kapo would-- would use his bullwhip and would hit these people hanging there to die, just hanging out like laundry.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Things like that which occurred there, later on you wouldn't even react to it anymore, because you yourself became an animal.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You weren't human being anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Your whole mind was set on getting extra food or-- or to survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Other people couldn't take it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would go out into the fence, which was the electric wire, which was loaded with about 5,000 volt of-- of electricity.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They just would electrocute themselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
